title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps the weekend in Sports. Should the Dolphins have allowed Tua to return after leaving with what appeared to be a concussion? And Ross Tucker joins us for his weekly appearance. Are the Eagles the best team in the NFC?
